<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Readiness Compass - {{ company_name }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a1a2e;
            --secondary: #16213e;
            --accent: #00d4ff;
            --success: #00ff88;
            --warning: #ffaa00;
            --danger: #ff4444;
            --text: #333;
            --text-light: #666;
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --bg-alt: #f8f9fa;
            --border: #e0e0e0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg);
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .report-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .report-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .report-header .company-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .report-header .meta {
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Score Section */
        .score-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .score-circle {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 6px solid {{ score_color }};
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .score-number {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: {{ score_color }};
        }

        .score-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .readiness-level {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .score-breakdown {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .breakdown-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .breakdown-value {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .breakdown-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* Section Styles */
        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Executive Summary */
        .executive-summary {
            background: var(--bg-alt);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .executive-summary p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .executive-summary p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Priority Cards */
        .priority-card {
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .priority-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .priority-rank {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .priority-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .priority-description {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .solution-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f7fa 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .solution-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .solution-name {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .solution-type {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .solution-detail {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .solution-detail strong {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .solution-tools {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .tool-tag {
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .impact-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--success);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .complexity-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .complexity-low {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }

        .complexity-medium {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }

        .complexity-high {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
        }

        /* Avoid Section */
        .avoid-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f5 0%, #ffe0e0 100%);
            border: 1px solid #ffcccc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .avoid-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .avoid-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background: var(--danger);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .avoid-name {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #721c24;
        }

        .avoid-tempting, .avoid-wrong {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid;
        }

        .avoid-tempting {
            border-color: var(--warning);
        }

        .avoid-wrong {
            border-color: var(--danger);
        }

        /* Roadmap Section */
        .roadmap-timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }

        .roadmap-timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 8px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--success) 100%);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .roadmap-phase {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--bg-alt);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .roadmap-phase::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -27px;
            top: 25px;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent);
        }

        .phase-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .phase-month {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .phase-focus {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .phase-actions {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .phase-actions li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .phase-actions li::before {
            content: '\2713';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .decision-gate {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--success) 0%, transparent 100%);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .report-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .report-footer .report-id {
            font-family: monospace;
            background: var(--bg-alt);
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Print Styles */
        @media print {
            body {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .score-section {
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                print-color-adjust: exact;
            }

            section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }

            .priority-card, .avoid-card, .roadmap-phase {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Report Header -->
    <header class="report-header">
        <h1>AI Readiness Compass</h1>
        <div class="company-name">{{ company_name }}</div>
        <div class="meta">{{ industry }} | {{ company_size }} employees</div>
        <div class="meta">Prepared for {{ contact_name }} | {{ generated_date }}</div>
    </header>

    <!-- AI Readiness Score -->
    <section class="score-section">
        <div class="score-circle">
            <span class="score-number">{{ score.overall_score|int }}</span>
            <span class="score-label">out of 100</span>
        </div>
        <div class="readiness-level">{{ readiness_level }} Level</div>
        <p>Your organization's AI implementation readiness</p>
        <div class="score-breakdown">
            <div class="breakdown-item">
                <div class="breakdown-value">{{ score.self_assessment_score|int }}</div>
                <div class="breakdown-label">Self-Assessment</div>
            </div>
            <div class="breakdown-item">
                <div class="breakdown-value">{{ score.research_score|int }}</div>
                <div class="breakdown-label">Research Score</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Executive Summary -->
    <section>
        <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
        <div class="executive-summary">
            {% for paragraph in executive_summary.split('\n\n') %}
            <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Top 3 Business Priorities -->
    <section>
        <h2>Top 3 Business Priorities</h2>
        {% for priority in priorities %}
        <div class="priority-card">
            <div class="priority-header">
                <span class="priority-rank">{{ priority.rank }}</span>
                <span class="priority-title">{{ priority.problem_name }}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="priority-description">{{ priority.problem_description }}</p>

            <div class="solution-box">
                <div class="solution-header">
                    <span class="solution-name">{{ priority.solution.name }}</span>
                    <span class="solution-type">{{ priority.solution.approach_type }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-detail">
                    <strong>Approach:</strong> {{ priority.solution.description }}
                </div>
                <div class="solution-detail">
                    <strong>Why This Fits:</strong> {{ priority.solution.why_this_fits }}
                </div>
                <div class="solution-tools">
                    <strong>Tools:</strong>
                    {% for tool in priority.solution.tools %}
                    <span class="tool-tag">{{ tool }}</span>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <span class="impact-badge">{{ priority.solution.expected_impact }}</span>
                    <span class="complexity-badge complexity-{{ priority.solution.complexity|lower }}">
                        {{ priority.solution.complexity }} Complexity
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <!-- What to Avoid -->
    <section>
        <h2>What to Avoid</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-light);">
            These solutions may seem attractive but are not right for your current readiness level.
        </p>
        {% for anti in avoid %}
        <div class="avoid-card">
            <div class="avoid-header">
                <span class="avoid-icon">!</span>
                <span class="avoid-name">{{ anti.name }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="avoid-tempting">
                <strong>Why It's Tempting:</strong> {{ anti.why_tempting }}
            </div>
            <div class="avoid-wrong">
                <strong>Why It's Wrong for You:</strong> {{ anti.why_wrong_for_them }}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <!-- 90-Day Implementation Roadmap -->
    <section>
        <h2>90-Day Implementation Roadmap</h2>
        <div class="roadmap-timeline">
            {% for phase in roadmap %}
            <div class="roadmap-phase">
                <div class="phase-header">
                    <span class="phase-month">Month {{ phase.month }}</span>
                    <span class="phase-focus">{{ phase.focus }}</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="phase-actions">
                    {% for action in phase.actions %}
                    <li>{{ action }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
                <div class="decision-gate">
                    <strong>Decision Gate:</strong> {{ phase.decision_gate }}
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Next Steps -->
    <section>
        <h2>Next Steps</h2>
        <div class="executive-summary">
            <p>
                <strong>Ready to start your AI journey?</strong> Based on your AI Readiness Score of
                {{ score.overall_score|int }}/100, we recommend beginning with Priority #1:
                {{ priorities[0].problem_name if priorities else 'your top business challenge' }}.
            </p>
            <p>
                The 90-day roadmap above provides a clear path forward. Start with Month 1's quick win
                to build momentum and demonstrate value to stakeholders.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Need help implementing?</strong> Contact us to discuss how we can support your
                AI implementation journey with hands-on guidance and technical expertise.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="report-footer">
        <p>AI Readiness Compass Report</p>
        <p>&copy; {{ year }} - All Rights Reserved</p>
        <div class="report-id">Report ID: {{ run_id }}</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
